channel.title: Money Making - Low Level
channel.description:
This isn't really much of a guide, but I'd thought I'd post this. This is a lower level method, but it can be done at any level.
So first off, you want to find a world with a lot of people at a cow pen. Once you've found a good world, you want to start collecting the Cowhide. I'd also recommend bringing some combat gear incase you want to speed up the trip. You should also bring some GP with you for the 10 GP Alkhaird gate (if you're doing the lumby cows).
As of now this is making around 7k per inventory. Which is really good for lower level players. I recently made a new OSRS account and made 40k in about an hour doing this method.
EDIT: You can also tan them for more money; however I don't recommend it as not many people buy them tanned.
